	"contentText": "Week 7\n  \n  \n  \n    Overview\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nRisk and risk premium, risk-free asset, portfolio algebra (storing return statistics in matrices and matrix operations), investment opportunity set, utility and risk aversion, optimal portfolio allocation with or without risk-free assets (minimum variance portfolio, efficient frontier, tangency portfolio, capital market line), Sharpe's ratio, solutions to the optimal portfolio allocation problem (formula for the optimal allocation between risk-free asset and tangency portfolio), one-fund separation results\n\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\nLearning Objectives\nUpon completion of this week, you will be able to understand:\n\nhow we measure absolute risk via return volatility or variance\nrisk premium as compensation for bearing risk\nhow to use matrices to store return statistics more efficiently\nthe role of risk aversion and utility\nhow to build the investment opportunity set of a given set of assets\nhow to build the efficient frontier of an investment opportunity set\nhow to find the tangency portfolio using Sharpe's ratio\nhow to find the optimal allocation between risk-free asset and the tangency portfolio\n\n \nPreparation for class\nMandatory reading:\nLecture 3: lecture 3.pdf\n    \n\nDownload lecture 3.pdf\nLecture 4: lecture 4.pdf\n    \n\nDownload lecture 4.pdf\n \nClass\nClass zoom link: Class logistics\n \nData work\ndata.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data.xlsx\ndata_prices.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data_prices.xlsx\ndata_work.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data_work.xlsx\ndata_work2.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data_work2.xlsx\n \nAssignments and Quizzes\nA3\n \nAdditional Resources\nChapter 6 and 7\n \nClass Notes\n\nSep 30 class recording: \nhttps://cuboulder.zoom.us/rec/share/VOaxKiRr4KeEe1Rjwrc5E-PdWxjpVK7a7atW09jMi19bBxoeLpd1yZVKeWJUYsdA.l1lHi3aYXZE0HkRL\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nPasscode: 2?NPD%v@\nClass work: data_work2.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data_work2.xlsx\n \nOct 2 class recording: \nhttps://cuboulder.zoom.us/rec/share/qh1siWj1Y7tlKbP8chdO4nooJbGE_heVkfBkzaz0GSFt2hgtIXReAsotdzuVNP8o.1xErs35AZDv85JAW\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nPasscode: G4U?TNX#\nClass work: data_work3.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data_work3.xlsx\n\n \n\n  \n  \n\n",
